original_title: Fleet Foxes Live on Boston Harbor
overview: On the Autumnal Equinox Sept 22, 2022, stream Fleet Foxes Live On Boston Harbor, a full band event. On the second anniversary of the GRAMMY nominated album's release, join us to celebrate + experience the Shore Tour + the Westerlies.
tagline: Streaming in celebration of the Autumnal Equinox and the second anniversary of "Shore"
title: Fleet Foxes Live on Boston Harbor
